{"word":"Ain","slug":"ain","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ain</b> <a href=\"#/H5871\">H5871</a> <br/> 1. A city of Simeon<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=7'>Jos 19:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=32'>Jos 15:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=16'>Jos 21:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=32'>1Ch 4:32</a> <br/> - Called Ashan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=59'>1Ch 6:59</a> <br/> - Possibly identical with En-Rimmon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=29'>Neh 11:29</a> <br/> 2. A landmark on the northern boundary of Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=11'>Num 34:11</a>"}]}